#: ../../language/error_codes/E4205.md:1
msgid "E4205"
msgstr "E4205"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4205.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `regex_map_key_not_supported`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`regex_map_key_not_supported`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4205.md:5
msgid "Regex literal is not supported as a map key."
msgstr "正则表达式字面量不能作为 map 键。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4205.md:7
msgid ""
"Map literals require ordinary key values. A `re\"...\"` literal creates a"
" `Regex`, and regex values are not valid map keys."
msgstr ""
"map 字面量需要普通的键值。`re\"...\"` 字面量会创建 `Regex`，而正则表达式值不"
"是有效的 map 键。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4205.md:10
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4205.md:12
msgid ""
"fn build_map() -> Unit {\n"
"  let _ = { re\"a+\": 1, \"b\": 2 }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4205.md:16
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4205.md:18
msgid ""
"Use a string key if you want to store the pattern text, or store regex "
"values as map values instead of keys."
msgstr ""
"如果要存储模式文本，请使用字符串键；或者将正则表达式值作为 map 值存储，而不是"
"作为键。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4205.md:21
msgid ""
"fn build_map() -> Unit {\n"
"  let _ = { \"a+\": 1, \"b\": 2 }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
